{"tid":965194,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"（ 尋同路人）有冇人童年既時候俾人非禮之後一直好驚人掂自己身體","createTime":"2019-01-02T00:24:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-03T06:51:49.000Z","uid":180913,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"73eecae1ee90bb3e40deaa89073bd58e25f94f64","tid":965194,"uid":180913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T00:24:22.000Z","msg":"認真post<br />\n今年有男仔有意思同我發展<br />\n現實中得兩位好朋友知我發生俾人非禮既事<br />\n我根本發生唔到性<br />\n發展黎到無意思，行唔到去結婚呢步<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁多年黎放棄左幾多次<br />\n所有電話都熄埋<br />\n只要有少少位（同 非禮者似樣同 觸碰到 某部位就會好驚恐）<br />\n我只係扮震定<br />\n外界只會見到我呆咗一呆<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今年新目標訂左去睇醫生<br />\n有冇人同路人<br />\n一入到去應該要點講<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n事情已經快20年了<br />\n連登仔唔需要me too<br />\n因為我係俾女同性戀者 非禮<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07d8d0d74321fbd4643acd93f7dcea4e67b09743","tid":965194,"uid":180913,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T00:33:33.000Z","msg":"如果我中左六合彩<br />\n我 第一時間唔係買樓<br />\n我一定會搵律師<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好想死<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 從來並未遇上好景降臨<br />\n我唔想同屋企人講<br />\n但係憑自己草錢要幾耐先草到？<br />\n永遠絕望<br />\n我有時諗 我斷氣嗰一刻<br />\n可以還到我一個公道？<br />\n我只想平淡 組織家庭<br />\n但夢想離我很遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aeb9af0de2e3c88ee5152b2b4e831a9c7d9b6382","tid":965194,"uid":180913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T00:34:49.000Z","msg":"原來 開錯咗地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef50d95a5d4de4a0d9d27d8c7a74b971890965b2","tid":965194,"uid":122139,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T00:37:10.000Z","msg":"俾你告到佢坐監你就冇事？"},{"pid":"bfa8d591a16a63e748765fde830c436ea6e9eb2d","tid":965194,"uid":177089,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T00:38:01.000Z","msg":"睇心理醫生"},{"pid":"198e340af1cd08859766c531fe3c1f8cbb3e317c","tid":965194,"uid":1751,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T00:38:20.000Z","msg":"拍拖好唔環保ga wor<br />\n做狗都唔會以污染自己個狗竇為榮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/01/235946_3a065c14cc2bcbd4eb03bcdd77991318.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F01%2F235946_3a065c14cc2bcbd4eb03bcdd77991318.png&h=7be82773&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/03/192852_c55bfca827914b85e2237a7b04a13847.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F03%2F192852_c55bfca827914b85e2237a7b04a13847.png&h=8b68fed6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MoYXFQ6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMoYXFQ6.png&h=216310d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jj0MOfG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fjj0MOfG.png&h=28005817&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n改名都無撚用<br />\n<br />\n麻煩其他人copy 番俾樓主睇，佢block 左我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91623203cd878860464b8ea236ee525ed10639a3","tid":965194,"uid":107364,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T00:38:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dcfd4cb381347d00d8f6ec1597d59edb71f69c7b","tid":965194,"uid":180913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bfa8d591a16a63e748765fde830c436ea6e9eb2d","tid":965194,"uid":177089,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T00:38:01.000Z","msg":"睇心理醫生"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":